msg: 你好啊！  (Nǐ hǎo a!)  What can I do for you today?  😊

name: Sakana
msg: 我是一个大型语言模型，由 Google 训练。  (Wǒ shì yīgè dàxíng yǔyán móxíng, yóu Google xùnliàn.)  I am a large language model, trained by Google.  In simpler terms, I'm a computer program that can understand and generate human-like text.  I can help you with various tasks, like answering questions, translating languages, writing different kinds of creative content, and much more.  What would you like to know or do?
